      "text": "あの友達と、どこで知り合ったのかって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where did I meet those friends?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 4.5666666348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "別に、普通だけど……SNSで繋がったとか\nよく行くバーでバイトしてた子に紹介されたとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing special… we connected on social media\nor introduced by someone working part-time at a bar I go to often.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3666666348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな忙しいし、あんまりしょっちゅうは遊べないけど\nって、なんであんたがkanaの友達気にしてる訳？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's busy‚ so we can't hang out very often.\nBut why are you concerned about kana's friends?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 22.6666650454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "なんというか……いい人達ですね\n芸能人のkanaさんを、特別扱いする感じでもないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How should I put it… they're good people.\nThey don't seem to treat you differently like a celebrity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "困ってたら、ああやって手伝いに来てくれるし\n俺にも着替えを貸してくれましたし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and when you're in trouble‚ they come help like that.\nThey even lent me a change of clothes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.7999983787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
