      "text": "そうそう。いい人達なのよ\n……あー、あんたの言いたいことなんとなく分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. They're good people.\n…Ah‚ I kind of understand what you want to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "いい人なのに、友達なのに\nなんで嘘くさい態度なんだ、とか言いたいんでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though they're good people‚ and good friends‚\nyou’re wondering why I acted so fake… right?",
        "id": ""
